{"tid":1797439,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「請鬼拿藥單」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-12-25T12:06:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T12:22:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5847f63c23a9a81ea41db44798955ae191308519","tid":1797439,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:06:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191225/20831008/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191225%2F20831008%2F&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFBOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=8367b7a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191225%2F20831008%2F&h=95100c5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191225/20831008/</a><br />\n<br />\n「請鬼拿藥單」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191225/large/1577180077_3bdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191225%2Flarge%2F1577180077_3bdd.jpg&h=7741680e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方宣傳片截圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港警察在facebook推出的宣傳片，看過的人都恥笑，賊喊捉賊已夠荒謬，賊當保安才真厚顏。<br />\n<br />\n影片先剪輯衝突片段，當然全屬示威者破壞，黑警皆不見了，而他們的任務是在慶祝聖誕佳節時，「守護大家珍而重之的和平」。情侶短訊更是天真幼稚之角色扮演，現實中催淚煙二噁英已潛藏大家體內，後遺症日漸浮現了，還裝作「不食人間煙火」？<br />\n<br />\n「BB出門未呀？」<br />\n<br />\n「香港近日咁亂，仲出唔出嚟好呀？」<br />\n<br />\n「唔使擔心，有香港警察保護我哋吖嘛&hellip;&hellip;點會有事發生？」<br />\n<br />\n正正因香港警察出現，才有事發生。黑警熱愛在鬧市商場民居濫發催淚彈噴椒，亂射布袋彈橡膠子彈，狂揮警棍威嚇，一不高興就發瘋般毒打、抓捕，到處推撞惡形惡相喝罵，實彈手槍指向市民（特別是老弱傷殘和婦孺），喬裝黑衣人插贓嫁禍喪盡天良，開車撞向人群恐襲竟休假復工，開槍後企圖抹掉指紋或砌詞被搶槍&hellip;&hellip;尋釁滋事滿手鮮血，保護市民？你叫我們信你靠你？真是「請鬼拿藥單」，自尋死路。<br />\n<br />\n總之，有黑警，和平拒門外；有防暴，財神不會來──這些物體不出現，香港普天同慶平安大吉。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"35cdb180a930c3365e1be7081f900406515ba217","tid":1797439,"uid":79916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:15:12.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"ab74ad1641360b4ded89bc266d6ad44de175b08b","tid":1797439,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fsin8-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/73099883_1111491312380530_6967407444922204160_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_ohc=hs4KjcDRv3IAQnpK8T0KFucdY0A7pA7j7AIp-BwZyFQARE7T0xmr4RllQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fsin8-1.fna&amp;oh=2d63c90e1f2f5a069ada96671071dc8c&amp;oe=5E66BA70\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fsin8-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F73099883_1111491312380530_6967407444922204160_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_ohc%3Dhs4KjcDRv3IAQnpK8T0KFucdY0A7pA7j7AIp-BwZyFQARE7T0xmr4RllQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fsin8-1.fna%26oh%3D2d63c90e1f2f5a069ada96671071dc8c%26oe%3D5E66BA70&h=4e16358a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}